# Touch & Drag - Quy tac

## Vi sao KHONG dung pointer absolute
Trong overlay, window di chuyen theo `anchor` moi tick. Neu gui pointer absolute
(`anchor - sprite_anchor + change.position`) thi:
- Window LayoutParams.x/y cap nhat **async** -> luc event toi co the dung gia tri cu.
- Engine ap `dragGrabOffset` HAI lan -> pet nhay xa hoac mat gesture.

## Pattern bat buoc: cumulative dragAmount + rememberUpdatedState

```kotlin
val snapState = rememberUpdatedState(snap)
Modifier.pointerInput(Unit) {
    var startX = 0f; var startY = 0f
    var totalDx = 0f; var totalDy = 0f
    detectDragGestures(
        onDragStart = {
            startX = snapState.value.anchorXPx
            startY = snapState.value.anchorYPx
            totalDx = 0f; totalDy = 0f
            eventSink.onPointerDown(startX, startY) // = anchor -> hit test pass + dragOffset = 0
        },
        onDrag = { change, dragAmount ->
            change.consume()
            totalDx += dragAmount.x
            totalDy += dragAmount.y
            eventSink.onPointerMove(startX + totalDx, startY + totalDy)
        },
        onDragEnd = { eventSink.onPointerUp() },
        onDragCancel = { eventSink.onPointerUp() },
    )
}
```

Ly do:
- `onDragStart` gui DUNG anchor -> `hitTestPointer` luon pass, `dragGrabOffset = 0`
  -> ngon tay luon nam tam window khi window dich theo, **khong rot gesture**.
- `dragAmount` la **delta tu lan truoc** (Compose) -> tich luy thanh `totalDx/Dy` de tao position cumulative.
- `rememberUpdatedState` giup lambda doc snapshot moi nhat ma KHONG restart pointerInput (giu gesture xuyen suot).

## Anti-pattern (cam)
- `pointerInput(snap)` -> snapshot doi moi tick -> gesture restart -> drag bi cancel.
- Goi truc tiep `repository.world.value` trong lambda (presentation khong duoc cham repository).
- Dung MotionEvent listener thay cho Compose (lop nay phai Compose-only).

## Khi them gesture moi (tap, long press, fling)
- Van qua `PetPlayEventSink` -> `DispatchPetInputUseCase` -> `PetEngine`.
- KHONG xu ly business logic (vi du "tap thi happy") trong Composable.
